data.description: Very motivated Seller for this beautiful 3 BR/2 bath home built in 2021 by Victory Builders being offered for sale in the sought after Covington Heights development off Woodleaf Road. Primary bedroom includes a walk in closet and dual sink bathroom. This home has a kitchen island with granite counter tops, shaker cabinets, stainless steel appliances, pantry, and laundry room.  This single level home sits on a flat roomy .66 acre lot with a concrete driveway. Schedule to view this home soon.
